OL,3,CStorm Dave: UK braces for jet stream-
OL,4,Cfuelled winds over the weekend
OL,6,FStorm Dave has been named as the UK
OL,7,Fbraces for jet stream-fuelled winds on
OL,8,FSaturday night.
OL,10,FBang on time for the Bank Holiday
OL,11,Fweekend, the Met Office said the storm
OL,12,Fis heading for the UK, bringing rain
OL,13,Fand winds gusting up to 90mph.
OL,15,FBut what can we expect? ITV News
OL,16,Fexplains
OL,18,FWhen does the stormy weather arrive
OL,19,Fand who will be worst affected?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
