OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775157064
OL,3,CStorm Dave: UK braces for jet stream-
OL,4,Cfuelled winds over the weekend
OL,6,FA deepening area of low pressure is
OL,7,Fexpected to sweep in from the
OL,8,FAtlantic, arriving across northwestern
OL,9,Fparts of the UK on Saturday evening
OL,10,Fand into the early hours of Sunday
OL,11,Fmorning.
OL,13,FThe worst affected areas are likely to
OL,14,Fbe across the northwest of the UK,
OL,15,Fparticularly west and northwestern
OL,16,FScotland.
OL,18,FHow bad will it be?
OL,20,FIt will be a widely windy night for
OL,21,Feveryone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
