FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775157064
OL,3,CStorm Dave: UK braces for jet stream-
OL,4,Cfuelled winds over the weekend
OL,6,FYellow wind warnings are in place
OL,7,Facross Scotland, Northern Ireland, the
OL,8,FNorth of England and northern Wales.
OL,10,FThese will come into force from
OL,11,FSaturday afternoon into Sunday.
OL,13,FWinds will widely gust around 50-60mph
OL,14,Facross the northwest but could reach
OL,15,F80-90mph in Scotland.
OL,17,FA yellow snow warning has also been
OL,18,Fissued for northwest Scotland on
OL,19,FSaturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
