PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775157064
OL,3,CStorm Dave: UK braces for jet stream-
OL,4,Cfuelled winds over the weekend
OL,6,FUp to 20cm of snow is possible, mostly
OL,7,Fover high ground.
OL,9,FWhy is it turning stormy?
OL,11,FIt's down to the powering up of the
OL,12,Fjet stream once again.
OL,14,FThe jet stream is a current of very
OL,15,Ffast moving air that sits in the upper
OL,16,Fatmosphere and acts like a conveyor
OL,17,Fbelt for low pressure systems.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775157064
OL,3,CStorm Dave: UK braces for jet stream-
OL,4,Cfuelled winds over the weekend
OL,6,FThe jet stream is being really powered
OL,7,Fup over the next few days because,
OL,8,Fonce again, there is a pool of very
OL,9,Fcold air sitting across Canada and
OL,10,FNorth America.
OL,12,FThe contrast between that cold air and
OL,13,Fthe comparatively warmer air further
OL,14,Fsouth is having boosting the speed and
OL,15,Fintensity of the jet stream which, in
OL,16,Fturn, "powers up" or deepens wind and
OL,17,Frain bearing low pressure systems that
OL,18,Fcross the Atlantic and head towards
OL,19,Fthe UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
