PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775157064
OL,3,CStorm Dave: UK braces for jet stream-
OL,4,Cfuelled winds over the weekend
OL,6,FPut simply, a powered up jet stream
OL,7,Fgives us "bigger" weather and the low
OL,8,Fpressure system that we're expecting
OL,9,Fto arrive on Saturday night, has the
OL,10,Fpotential to be deeper and more
OL,11,Fimpactful that it might otherwise be.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FWhy have the storms this year not
OL,19,Ffollowed the Met Office's list of
OL,20,Fstorm names?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775157064
OL,3,CStorm Dave: UK braces for jet stream-
OL,4,Cfuelled winds over the weekend
OL,6,FThis is a very common question as it
OL,7,Fcauses widespread confusion. This is
OL,8,Fbecause it's not just the Met Office
OL,9,F(the UK's national weather service)
OL,10,Fthat names storms!
OL,12,FStorms can also be named by the
OL,13,Fnational weather services of other
OL,14,Fcountries who have their own list of
OL,15,Fnames.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775157064
OL,3,CStorm Dave: UK braces for jet stream-
OL,4,Cfuelled winds over the weekend
OL,6,FThe published list of names from the
OL,7,FMet Office for this storm season (up
OL,8,Fto the letter D) are Amy, Bram,
OL,9,FChandra and Dave - and yet we've also
OL,10,Fhad Storm Benjamin (named by
OL,11,FMeteoFrance on 22 October 2025),
OL,12,FStorm Claudia (named by Spain's AEMET
OL,13,Fon 10 November 2025) and Storm Goretti
OL,14,F(named by MeteoFrance on 6 January
OL,15,F2026).
OL,17,FIt's not a perfect system but the
OL,18,Fupshot is the same; all storms are
OL,19,Fnamed to increase awareness of
OL,20,Fpotential impacts to the public.
OL,26,@sD@BrrsD@DrrvD@LrrvD@Nrr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
