OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775157064
OL,3,CStorm Dave: UK braces for jet stream-
OL,4,Cfuelled winds over the weekend
OL,6,FHas the Met Office issued any warnings
OL,7,Fyet?
OL,9,FYes ` yellow warnings are already in
OL,10,Fplace for strong winds over the Easter
OL,11,Fweekend.
OL,13,FThese warnings highlight the increased
OL,14,Frisk of travel disruption, difficult
OL,15,Fdriving conditions, and possible
OL,16,Flocalised impacts such as fallen
OL,17,Fbranches or temporary power issues.
OL,19,FMake sure you stay up to date with the
OL,20,Fforecast for the very latest on this
OL,21,Fdeveloping situation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
